      <title>Re: Rules regarding macroing</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=TNZ&amp;message.id=227137#M227137</link>
      <description>There is a way to run in circule but only a tight circle.  If you are pressing forward and left or right (not using Autorun) then you start typing, your toon will keep running.  Square, triangles, other geometric shape or large circle (ie kiting circle) can't be done automatically within the game, only from external devices which may be illegal.&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
