owed up when he was there. And since he replied to a tell, i was told it was all fine and dandy. Even tho it was CLEARLY visible, that he did things the ingame hotkeys do NOT allow (autofollow a mob with autoattack on, not ranged attack like sugessted here)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;If i petition with a link to this topic, might that work? I understand that not all GMs can know all grey areas of every rule. Your answers here a clear and straight, so there is not a single doubt: he IS indeed doing alot of things that are NOT allowed.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Thanks for the reply, really made my day... now onto to find a GM that knows the same answers hehe.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
